1. Why should you find ways to empathize with your customer through design research?
Solution : B. To truly understand your customer and judge if your solution will make a difference in their lives

2. What are three common forms of empathic research methods to gain deep insight into your customers?
Solution : A. Embodying, shadowing, and interviewing

3. You should shadow someone to:
Solution : D. Directly observe their behavior in person
